cmd:
apiVersion: chaos-mesh.org/v1alpha1
kind: HTTPChaos
metadata:
  name: pod-http-request-delay.ts-travel2-service
  namespace: default
spec:
  delay: 500ms
  duration: 300s
  mode: one
  path: '*'
  port: 16346
  selector:
    labelSelectors:
      app: ts-travel2-service
    namespaces:
    - default
  target: Request

apiVersion: chaos-mesh.org/v1alpha1
kind: HTTPChaos
metadata:
  name: svc-http-request-delay.ts-rebook-service
  namespace: default
spec:
  delay: 500ms
  duration: 300s
  mode: all
  path: '*'
  port: 18886
  selector:
    labelSelectors:
      app: ts-rebook-service
    namespaces:
    - default
  target: Request
